  <hr />
  <div class="post-item"><span class="tag tag-mystery">海洋</span> <a href={`${BASE}mystery/mystery-001/`} target="_blank"><strong>百慕大三角海域异常</strong></a> <span class="text-muted">大西洋 | 更新于 2025-12-15</span></div>
  <div class="post-item"><span class="tag tag-mystery">地外</span> <a href={`${BASE}mystery/mystery-002/`} target="_blank"><strong>麦田怪圈之谜</strong></a> <span class="text-muted">英国·威尔特郡 | 更新于 2025-12-20</span></div>
